  "task" : "Implement a feature based on the team reports. It is finally a time to code, yay!\n\nBut first check and fix any bug reports from existing code in `deployment.log` (if any).\n\nScope ~500-1000 lines per each coding session - this is a good practice to follow to limit a risk of breaking things.\nMake sure that whatever you are building is connected to existing code and is usable (unless it is in WIP status).\nAddress existing TODOs in a code related to a feature that you are actively working on.\n\nWhen you leave a feature in \"wip\" status make sure to update project's AGENTS.md file with a status.",
